Contains the classes needed for error reporting for railway systems.

  • Exception Summary

    ProgrammingError
    An error has occured that suggests a programming error.

    SafetyViolationError

    SetUpError
    An error has occured while trying to set up the system.

Package ferrocarrilesDeAmericaDelSur.errors Description

Contains the classes needed for error reporting for railway systems. The currently are:
  • A general railway system error class.
  • Errors seemingly caused by programming errors.
  • Errors seemingly caused by incorrect values for set-up parameters.
  • Errors seemingly caused by safety violations during a run of a railway system.
